title: Georgia Tech women advance to ACC quarterfinals -  The Atlanta Journal Constitution
content: Georgia Tech women advance to ACC quarterfinals   The Atlanta Journal Constitution
description: Georgia Tech made an early statement and built a double-digit lead over Wake Forest in Thursday night’s ACC tournament game by leaning on its strength — stout interior defense and offensive movement. On the first possession of the second quarter, however, it got a lot tougher for the Jackets in Greensboro, N.C.
